Package edu.usc.scrc.PriorityPruner

Class Summary
ChrPValueSorter This sorter sorts SNPs by chromosome and base pair position.
CommandLineOptions This class defines and parses the command line options given as input to the program.
FIChrPValueSorter This sorter sorts SNPs in regards to if they are force included, then by chromosome and position.
ForceIncludePValueSorter Sorts SNPs in regards to if they are force included and then by p-value.
Genotypes This is the superclass of the different input formats that eventually will be implemented.
Individual This class stores the family information for a certain individual.
LdResult This class stores the LD information for each result calculated between two SNPs.
LogWriter This class handles the logging of PriorityPruner by using the Apache Commons Log4j library.
Metric This class stores the name and weight of a metric.
MetricNamePos This class helps SnpListFile keep track of the order that metrics where entered in the SNP input file.
PosSorter Sorts SnpInfo-objects in regards to chromosome and position.
PriorityPruner This is the main class of PriorityPruner.
Pruner This class is responsible for pruning and prioritizing the SNPs defined in the input files.
R2Threshold This class stores an r^2 threshold together with its associated p-value.
Result This class represents a result record between a pair of SNPs.
ScoreSorter Sorts Result-objects in regards to if they are force included, have passed design score, their number of bead types, their score and name.
SnpGenotypes This class stores all available information for a certain SNP.
SnpInfo This class stores information about a certain SNP.
SnpListFile This class handles both the parsing of the SNP input file, as well as the comparison between it and the TPlink data.
SnpR2Pair This class is used to easily store a SNP together with an associated r^2 value.
SnpWorkUnit This class is used to find all the SNPs (in the given search range) that are in LD.
SurrogateThreshold This class stores the desired number of surrogates together with an associated p-value.
TPlink This class handles the parsing of the transposed plink-formats: tped & tfam.
 

Exception Summary
PriorityPrunerException Custom exception for PriorityPruner, used throughout the program.
